OL,3,C'Heinous' assault robbed innocent
OL,4,Cchild of sight, speech and independence
OL,6,FThe foster parent now looking after a
OL,7,Fchild who suffered a long list of
OL,8,Fcatastrophic and life limiting
OL,9,Finjuries has told a Newry Court that
OL,10,Fhe is a totally "innocent victim of a
OL,11,Fheinous crime".
OL,13,FChristopher Fulton, 35, of Maghaberry
OL,14,Fprison and Amanda Fulton, 36, of
OL,15,FRockfield Gardens in Mosside have been
OL,16,Fawaiting sentencing since they were
OL,17,Fconvicted by a jury in October.
