OL,6,FAmanda Fulton was acquitted of GBH
OL,7,Fwith intent and one charge of child
OL,8,Fcruelty, but she was unanimously
OL,9,Fconvicted of causing or allowing the
OL,10,Fchild to suffer significant physical
OL,11,Fharm and a further charge of child
OL,12,Fcruelty in relation to wilful neglect.
OL,14,FOn Friday, Judge Peter Irvine KC
OL,15,Fallowed the harrowing victim impact
OL,16,Fassessment to be read directly to the
OL,17,Fcourt, using his discretion to grant
OL,18,Fwhat is believed to be a first in
OL,19,FNorthern Ireland.
