OL,4,Cchild of sight, speech and independence
OL,6,FThat statement outlined how the child
OL,7,Fhas never spoken a single word, has
OL,8,Fbeen "robbed of the ability to see",
OL,9,Fis tube-fed, and his life will be
OL,10,Flimited by the litany of severe
OL,11,Finjuries he has suffered.
OL,13,F"His life is one of constant medical
OL,14,Fappointments, each confirming how
OL,15,Fdisabled he is," they said.
OL,17,FThey went on to spell out the life the
OL,18,Fboy would never know.
