OL,6,F"He will never see the sunrise. He
OL,7,Fwill never know what the ocean looks
OL,8,Flike. He will never see the toys that
OL,9,FSanta left for him under the tree."
OL,11,FThe court heard how the very young
OL,12,Fchild was unresponsive on the morning
OL,13,Fof 7 November 2019 at Fulton's home
OL,14,Fbut despite their concerns neither
OL,15,Fdefendant called a doctor for three
OL,16,Fhours.
